&lt;h3 id="appscript-part"&gt;Appscript Part
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;By copying this sheet you will also get the code for the setup, I will explain later in the blog.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have a basic sheet setup. Fill the details for the website and renew the date accordingly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-test-properly"&gt;How to Test Properly
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;First Test the main function by running in the editor. It will show unverified because you have not verified this app on google cloud, No problem you will need to click on Advance. Then click the unsafe option. No Problem you can verify your script later.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will not remind automatically, We need to set up a trigger for the function.&lt;/p&gt;
