&lt;p&gt;This tutorial describes how to automate the slack messages with google apps script for free of cost.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This tutorial describes how to automate the slack messages with google apps script for free of cost. Yes you read it right, We do not need the server for the webhooks of slack.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-is-the-webhook-of-slack"&gt;What is the webhook of slack?
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Slack Webhook allows users to send data to slack easily from outside APIs or resources. This can be a very useful feature to make a better notification system. You do not need to go through the email for important notification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="create-a-google-apps-script-project"&gt;Create a google apps script project
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;googleappscript.gs&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
